## Prerequisites

- [Go 1.23+](https://go.dev/dl/)
- [PostgreSQL 15+](https://www.postgresql.org/download/)[[ if .HasMigrations ]]
- [goose](https://github.com/pressly/goose) (database migrations)[[ end ]][[ if .HasDBTooling ]]
- [sqlc](https://sqlc.dev/) (SQL code generation)[[ end ]]

## Quick Start

```bash
# Copy environment file and edit as needed
cp .env.example .env

# Install dependencies
go mod download
[[ if .HasMigrations ]]
# Run database migrations
make migrate-up
[[ end ]]
# Build and run
make run
```

The server starts on `http://localhost:8080` by default.

## API Endpoints

| Method   | Path                  | Description             |
|----------|-----------------------|-------------------------|
| `GET`    | `/healthz`            | Liveness probe          |
| `GET`    | `/readyz`             | Readiness probe         |[[ if .HasDatabase ]]
| `POST`   | `/api/resources`      | Create a resource       |
| `GET`    | `/api/resources`      | List all resources      |
| `GET`    | `/api/resources/{id}` | Get a resource by ID    |
| `PUT`    | `/api/resources/{id}` | Update a resource       |
| `DELETE` | `/api/resources/{id}` | Delete a resource       |[[ end ]]

## Make Targets

| Target         | Description                          |
|----------------|--------------------------------------|
| `build`        | Build the binary                     |
| `run`          | Build and run the service            |
| `test`         | Run tests with race detector         |
| `lint`         | Run golangci-lint                    |[[ if .HasMigrations ]]
| `migrate-up`   | Apply database migrations            |
| `migrate-down` | Rollback last migration              |[[ end ]][[ if .HasDBTooling ]]
| `generate`     | Run sqlc code generation             |[[ end ]][[ if .HasContainer ]]
| `docker-build` | Build Docker image                   |
| `docker-run`   | Build and run in Docker              |[[ end ]]
| `clean`        | Remove binary and test cache         |

